title: Hour 3 - Eagles/Texans + Phillies/Astros, John Smoltz
itunes:title: Hour 3 - Eagles/Texans + Phillies/Astros, John Smoltz
description:
Dan wonders who Philadelphians would rather watch as their NFL and MLB teams both match up against squads from Houston tonight. And he talks to Hall of Fame Pitcher and FOX World Series Analyst, John Smoltz about whether last night's game should count as a no-hitter for the Astros.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
